flowRoot.flowPara: Risk levels of GAVI countries due to number and duration of DTP stock-outs(SOs). Medium risk countries had 3 or more total counts or avg duration of SOs. High risk countries had 3 or more total counts and athat had vg3 or more DTP stock-outs or an average of 3 or more months stock-outs from 2005 to 2012. 18 countries out of 72 fit this profile. Low risk countries not shown.
Authors: David S Opoku & Benjamin Schreiber | Jan 2014
Data source: Joint Reporting Form | Patrick Lydon
